OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775495152
OL,3,CTeenager charged following disorder
OL,4,Cbefore Irish Cup semi-final match in
OL,5,CBelfast
OL,7,FA 19-year-old man has been charged
OL,8,Fwith riotous behaviour following
OL,9,Fdisorder before the Irish Cup semi-
OL,10,Ffinal match in Belfast.
OL,12,FPolice said a child was hit by a
OL,13,Fbottle and nine officers were injured
OL,14,Fas fireworks, flares and bottles were
OL,15,Fthrown in the scenes at Windsor Park
OL,16,Fon Friday evening.
OL,18,FIt came before the match between north
OL,19,FBelfast side Cliftonville and
OL,20,FDungannon Swifts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
