PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775495152
OL,3,CTeenager charged following disorder
OL,4,Cbefore Irish Cup semi-final match in
OL,5,CBelfast
OL,7,FA number of Cliftonville supporters
OL,8,Fhad taken part in a parade ahead of
OL,9,Fthe clash, which Swifts won on
OL,10,Fpenalties after a 1-1 draw.
OL,12,FThe man has been charged with riotous
OL,13,Fbehaviour, doing a provocative act,
OL,14,Fpossession of fireworks/flares at a
OL,15,Fregulated match, indecent behaviour
OL,16,Fand attempted criminal damage.
OL,18,FHe is due to appear before Belfast
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on May 1.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
